    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a high level of operational tempo, with multiple aircraft and vessels engaged in various missions worldwide. The presence of carrier strike groups, amphibious ready groups, forward-deployed destroyers, cruisers, and submarines indicates a significant naval presence. The aerial refueling fleet is also heavily engaged, supporting a wide range of aircraft operations. The ongoing Operation Epic Fury has resulted in a significant increase in military activity, with multiple countries involved and a high risk of escalation. The threat posed by Iranian air defenses and the use of drones by Iran-backed militias are significant concerns for military planners. Overall, the current military situation is complex and dynamic, with multiple factors at play and a high level of uncertainty.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
    </Folder>
